            <lb/>administrateur de Jehan pierre Jehan et Jacques <persName>andre</persName> ses enffens
            <lb/>Jehan et hellies <persName>de valbrune</persName> pere et filz <expan>appellans</expan> du seneschal de
            <lb/>perigort ou son <expan>lieutenant</expan> anticippans et <expan>aultrement</expan> appelles <choice><orig>dune</orig><reg>d’une</reg></choice> part
            <lb/>Et <expan>maitre</expan><persName>pierre du boys</persName><choice><orig>aduocat</orig><reg>advocat</reg></choice> au siege presidial de <placeName>perigueulx</placeName> et
            <lb/><persName><forename>blandelize</forename><nameLink>de</nameLink><surname>saulliere</surname></persName> damoiselle sa femme anticippans <expan>et</expan><expan>aultrement</expan><lb/><expan>appellans</expan><expan>dudit</expan> seneschal ou <expan>sondit</expan> lieutenant <choice><orig>daultre</orig><reg>d’aultre</reg></choice></ab><ab><lb/>Veu le proces libelz appellatoyres responces a iceulx
            <lb/>recusations presantees par Jehan et hellies de <persName>valbrune</persName> contre Les
            <lb/><del><expan>conseilliers</expan></del> magistras et <expan>conseilliers</expan> du siege presidial de <placeName>perigueulx</placeName><lb/>du septiesme aougt mil cinq cens cinquante <expan>et</expan> sept <expan>et</expan> vingtdeuzieme
            <lb/><choice><orig>apuril</orig><reg>apvril</reg></choice> mil cinq cens soixante <expan>et</expan> ung discution faicte entre
            <lb/>les parties du vingtquatrieme may mil cinq cens <expan>cinquante</expan><expan>et</expan> neuf
            <lb/><expan>et</expan><expan>aultres</expan> pieces <expan>et</expan> production <expan>desdites</expan> parties
          </ab><ab><lb/>Il sera dit <choice><orig>auant</orig><reg>avant</reg></choice> procedder au <expan>jugement</expan><expan>dudit</expan> proces que ledict
            <lb/><persName>andre</persName> veriffira a paine de cinquante <choice><orig>liures</orig><reg>livres</reg></choice> aplicables moytie
            <lb/>au roy <expan>et</expan> moictie a la partye dedans ung moys <expan>prochainement</expan><lb/>venant <expan>pardevant</expan> le commissaire qui par la court sur ce <expan>sera</expan> deppute
            <lb/>que les biens vacquans de feue chalup mesme ceulx <expan>que</expan><expan>ledit</expan><lb/><persName>du boys</persName> et <persName>saulliere</persName> sa femme ont faict mectre en criee
            <lb/>par la derniere execution de laquelle est question ou
            <lb/><expan>present</expan> proces sont plus que suffizans pour le <expan>paiement</expan> tant
            <lb/>des arreraiges <expan>que</expan> du principal de la rente pretandue
            <lb/>par <expan>ledit</expan><persName>du boys</persName> Et <expan>lesdits</expan><persName>du boys</persName><expan>et</expan><persName>saulliere</persName><pb facs="http://www.bvh.univ-tours.fr/FRAD0330635101_1B280_118/ecran/FRAD0330635101_1B280_118_0002.jpg" n="0002" xml:id="FRAD0330635101_1B280_118_0002"/><fw type="pageNum">[f. 118v]</fw><lb/>au contrayre si bon leur samble pour ce faict <expan>et</expan> le tout
            <lb/>par <choice><orig>deuers</orig><reg>devers</reg></choice> la court rapportee<del>s</del><del>estre faict droict</del><lb/><del>aux <space quantity="10" unit="mm"/></del> estre procedde ainsi que de raison despens
            <lb/><choice><orig>reserues</orig><reg>reserves</reg></choice> en fin de cause
          </ab><ab rend="left" type="signature"><handShift new="#MainLDA"/><lb/><persName>Alesme</persName></ab><ab rend="center"><lb/><foreign xml:lang="lat"><expan>habeat</expan> relator <expan>pro</expan><expan>specibus</expan><lb/>duodecim scuta. Et
            <lb/><expan>pro</expan><expan>commissariis</expan> quadraginta
            <lb/><expan>unum</expan><expan>scutum</expan> de quibus
            <lb/>soluet tertiam <expan>partem</expan><lb/>dictus <persName>andre</persName> saluo de
            <lb/>recuperando</foreign></ab><ab corresp="#MainMDM" rend="left" type="signature"><handShift new="#MainMDM"/><lb/><persName><forename>michel</forename><nameLink>de</nameLink><choice><orig>mōtaigne</orig><reg>montaigne</reg></choice></persName><foreign xml:lang="lat">relator</foreign></ab><ab corresp="#MainMDM" rend="right"><lb/><expan>messieurs</expan><choice><orig>presidās</orig><reg>presidans</reg></choice><list><item><expan><persName><choice><orig>dalesme</orig><reg>d’alesme</reg></choice></persName></expan></item><item><persName>la guionie</persName></item></list><lb/><choice><abbr>cōs.</abbr><expan>conseillers</expan></choice><list><item><persName><choice><orig>deimar</orig><reg>d’eimar</reg></choice></persName></item><item><persName>du duc</persName></item><item><persName>massei</persName></item><item><persName>de alis</persName></item><item><persName>casaus</persName></item><item><persName>rignac</persName></item><item><persName>macanan</persName></item><item><persName>de merle</persName></item><item><persName>faïard</persName></item><item><persName><choice><orig>mōtaigne</orig><reg>montaigne</reg></choice></persName><choice><abbr>rap.</abbr><expan>rapporteur</expan></choice></item></list></ab><lb/><lb/><ab rend="center" type="signature"><handShift new="#MainX2"/><lb/><date when="1565-04-14">XIIIIe <choice><orig>dauril</orig><reg>d’avril</reg></choice> mVCLXIIII 
